{"id":660964,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2021/01/有所读｜五条人和谭维维的歌词篡改：没有意义改/","date":"2021-01-01T10:24:35Z","modified":"2021-01-01T10:24:35Z","title":"有所读｜五条人和谭维维的歌词篡改：没有意义改没有异议，翻白眼改放白烟","content":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1cc683f7.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>b站和江苏卫视跨年演唱会，注意到五条人和谭维维的歌词字幕被篡改。虽说演唱歌词被改，好像司空见惯。不过看到谭维维的歌词，被改得厉害，确实惊了。整理出来。</p>\n<p>b站，五条人《阿珍爱上了阿强》，“人生并没有什么意义”改成“人生并没有什么异议”。江苏卫视，谭维维《钱夫人》，“肤浅”改“付钱”，“禽兽”改成“情瘦”，“翻白眼” 改“放白烟”，“良心分两半”改“内心分两半”，“你招摇要撞骗”改“你张扬又装扁”，“认了命的污染” 改“认了命的屋檐”，“老娘敬老天”改成“老梁敬老田”；虞书欣和赵小棠合唱《卡门》，“男人都喜欢”改“爱情都喜欢”。</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>1.b站跨年，五条人《阿珍爱上了阿强》歌词篡改</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1ce4f57c.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“人生并没有什么意义”改“人生并没有什么异议”</p>\n<p><strong>2.江苏卫视跨年，谭维维《钱夫人》歌词篡改</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1cfe2b42.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“看谁等肤浅”改“看谁等付钱”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1d1c60da.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“良心分两半”改“内心分两半”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1d3a668c.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“禽兽”改“情瘦”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1d59bd64.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“翻白眼” 改“放白烟”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1d7d3ba3.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“老娘敬老天”改成“老梁敬老田”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1cc683f7.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“招摇又撞骗”改“ 张扬又装扁”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2021/01/post-660964-5feef1dbe70c3.\" alt=\"img\" width=\"500\"></p>\n<p>“认了命的污染” 改“认了命的屋檐”</p>\n","author":1057,"categories":[18271,41492,38912],"tags":[42304,42597,14804,42515]}